
    Code introduction : 
        scripts in this folder is used to train H2O force model from 
        CP2K dataset (from Yihao), Include core force and force of 
        wannier center. 

    ===============================================================================
       Code name                       Discription
    -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      Split_data.py         Split Yihao's cp2k dataset to single config
       Get_Ewald.py         Calculate long range force in H2O system 
    Produce_features.cpp    Calculate BPNN features 
    Data_pretreatment.py    Calculate features and generate Train & Valid dataset
    Train_data_ptepate.py   Do nothing yet :>
    ===============================================================================
